               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250113-42-cd205" type="crimeDate">18th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250113-42-off204 t18250113-42-cd205"></join>, an iron boiler, value 10 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18250113-42-victim285" type="victimName">
                  Joseph 
                  Reynolds
               <interp inst="t18250113-42-victim285" type="surname" value="Reynolds"></interp>
